NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN that St Francis Hospital located at 34515 9th Ave Federal Way WA 98003 claims a
lien, as a hospital, in accordance with Section 60.44.010 through 60.44.060 of the Revised Code of Washington, for
the furnishing of emergency, medical, or other service on or about 6/6/2021 through 6/6/2021 to the following
patient:
Name: Baclay, Sherrilene V M
Mailing Address: 2008 S 327th Ln, Apt S101 Federal Way WA 98003
Residence Address: [If no Residence Address listed, residence is same as Mailing Address]
On 6/6/2021 at S 320TH ST the above-named Patient sustained traumatic personal injuries allegedly caused by the
tort-feasor listed below and sought treatment for said injuries at St Francis Hospital The hospital lien claimed by St
Francis Hospitalis upon any claim, right of action, and/or money to which the patient is entitled from the tort-
feasor(s) and/or any insurer(s) of such tort-feasor(s) for the value of such service, together with costs and such
reasonable attorney's fees as the court may allow, incurred in enforcing such lien. The names and addresses of the
tort-feasor(s), if known, alleged to be liable for the damages arising from said injury are:
WENDELL COX
UNKNOWN
Unofficial Copy
As of the date of filing, the amount of hospital charges subject to this lien total $10,362.98. Additional charges may
be incurred prior to payment of damages.
